{
  "video_id": "WKlIyta-lu4",
  "title": "The role of faith and belief in modern Africa | Ndidi Nwuneli",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12513.0,
      "end_time": 16620.0,
      "text": "I was born to two amazing professors who were not religious."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17439.0,
      "end_time": 19813.0,
      "text": "In fact, my father&#39;s regular response"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19837.0,
      "end_time": 23837.0,
      "text": "to the question about why we didn&#39;t go to church on Sundays was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23861.0,
      "end_time": 27980.0,
      "text": "\"When others go to pray, I go to play.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27122.0,
      "end_time": 29521.0,
      "text": "Tennis, in case you&#39;re wondering."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30340.0,
      "end_time": 34486.0,
      "text": "Faith found me and my siblings when university students came to our house"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 34510.0,
      "end_time": 36339.0,
      "text": "to invite us to Sunday school."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36875.0,
      "end_time": 40680.0,
      "text": "I was drawn by their sense of personal conviction"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 40704.0,
      "end_time": 42725.0,
      "text": "and their life of service,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 42749.0,
      "end_time": 45996.0,
      "text": "and opted for baptism into the Christian faith"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 46200.0,
      "end_time": 48780.0,
      "text": "as my 10th birthday present."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48634.0,
      "end_time": 52222.0,
      "text": "My faith has shaped my work as a social entrepreneur,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 52246.0,
      "end_time": 54888.0,
      "text": "attempting to address Africa&#39;s most pressing challenges"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 54912.0,
      "end_time": 57238.0,
      "text": "over the last 17 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 57262.0,
      "end_time": 61126.0,
      "text": "and my work training youth as leaders"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 61150.0,
      "end_time": 63532.0,
      "text": "and promoting ethics across Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 65930.0,
      "end_time": 66699.0,
      "text": "Twenty-nine years later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 66724.0,
      "end_time": 69148.0,
      "text": "as a Sunday school teacher myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 69172.0,
      "end_time": 72886.0,
      "text": "my faith was challenged by a young nine-year-old"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 72910.0,
      "end_time": 74771.0,
      "text": "who asked a series of questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 75895.0,
      "end_time": 77423.0,
      "text": "He asked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 77447.0,
      "end_time": 80876.0,
      "text": "\"Ms. Ndidi, does God hate Africans?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 82345.0,
      "end_time": 84568.0,
      "text": "To which I quickly retorted, \"Of course not."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 84592.0,
      "end_time": 86774.0,
      "text": "God loves all his children equally.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 87634.0,
      "end_time": 91284.0,
      "text": "Then he asked, \"So why do so many young African children die?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 92685.0,
      "end_time": 95740.0,
      "text": "I stumbled and mumbled as I responded."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 95530.0,
      "end_time": 98803.0,
      "text": "\"There are many reasons why young African children die."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 99491.0,
      "end_time": 102504.0,
      "text": "Most of them are man-made, and we cannot blame God.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 103533.0,
      "end_time": 106134.0,
      "text": "So he asked, \"Why does he let it happen?"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 106158.0,
      "end_time": 107314.0,
      "text": "He could stop it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 107859.0,
      "end_time": 109900.0,
      "text": "And I said ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 109973.0,
      "end_time": 112210.0,
      "text": "\"Yes he could, yes he could,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 112450.0,
      "end_time": 114943.0,
      "text": "but he sent us here as change agents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 114967.0,
      "end_time": 117588.0,
      "text": "light of the world, salt of the earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 117612.0,
      "end_time": 118875.0,
      "text": "and we are failing.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 120839.0,
      "end_time": 124404.0,
      "text": "Africa has had a mixed affair with organized religion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 124428.0,
      "end_time": 127340.0,
      "text": "with both positive and negative consequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 128624.0,
      "end_time": 132109.0,
      "text": "The Christian missionaries educated most of our political elite,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 132133.0,
      "end_time": 134220.0,
      "text": "like Senghor and Nkrumah,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 134244.0,
      "end_time": 137647.0,
      "text": "built many of our first hospitals and schools."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 138747.0,
      "end_time": 144849.0,
      "text": "Similarly, Islam has introduced commerce and mathematics"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 144873.0,
      "end_time": 146268.0,
      "text": "across the continent."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 147372.0,
      "end_time": 152848.0,
      "text": "Today, we have over a billion Africans who profess a strong faith."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 154443.0,
      "end_time": 158136.0,
      "text": "What is the net effect of this on our continent?"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 159155.0,
      "end_time": 163830.0,
      "text": "A recent \"Economist\" article said that the face of the future"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 163854.0,
      "end_time": 166836.0,
      "text": "of the world&#39;s most popular religion is African."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 168400.0,
      "end_time": 173558.0,
      "text": "Now, both Islam and Christianity underscore the importance of social impact"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 173582.0,
      "end_time": 175525.0,
      "text": "as critical tenets of our faith."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 176983.0,
      "end_time": 180929.0,
      "text": "Muhammad is noted for stating"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 180953.0,
      "end_time": 185238.0,
      "text": "that he is not a believer who goes to bed on a full stomach"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 185262.0,
      "end_time": 187453.0,
      "text": "when his neighbor to his side is hungry."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 188456.0,
      "end_time": 190358.0,
      "text": "And all through the New Testament,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 190383.0,
      "end_time": 193311.0,
      "text": "Jesus Christ talks about loving your neighbors as yourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 194654.0,
      "end_time": 197567.0,
      "text": "giving to the poor, caring for the sick,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 198604.0,
      "end_time": 202209.0,
      "text": "and James, too, says that \"faith without works is dead.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 203236.0,
      "end_time": 208569.0,
      "text": "So I strongly believe that faith-based organizations have a critical role to play"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 208593.0,
      "end_time": 210617.0,
      "text": "in driving social impact in Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 211321.0,
      "end_time": 215551.0,
      "text": "But for this to occur, we need three critical changes."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 216355.0,
      "end_time": 218932.0,
      "text": "The first is that we need to change our mindsets."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 219983.0,
      "end_time": 223515.0,
      "text": "Both as people of faith and of those who are not religious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 223539.0,
      "end_time": 226265.0,
      "text": "their perceptions of those of us who are people of faith."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 227471.0,
      "end_time": 231657.0,
      "text": "Now, for people of faith and those of us who are religious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 231681.0,
      "end_time": 234488.0,
      "text": "we often say, \"If God wills, I&#39;ll do this;"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 234512.0,
      "end_time": 236798.0,
      "text": "inshallah, I&#39;ll do that --"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 236822.0,
      "end_time": 238980.0,
      "text": "by God&#39;s grace, I&#39;ll do this.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 239988.0,
      "end_time": 244840.0,
      "text": "Now there are many things, I believe, that we can control --"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 244108.0,
      "end_time": 245360.0,
      "text": "some we cannot."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 246431.0,
      "end_time": 248435.0,
      "text": "I believe that God is all-powerful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 248459.0,
      "end_time": 250230.0,
      "text": "but he&#39;s not a micromanager."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 251660.0,
      "end_time": 253580.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 253820.0,
      "end_time": 256305.0,
      "text": "He has sent us here as his change agents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 256329.0,
      "end_time": 258209.0,
      "text": "and we must stop making excuses"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 258233.0,
      "end_time": 259385.0,
      "text": "and using him."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 260478.0,
      "end_time": 262828.0,
      "text": "That means that if you&#39;re a teacher,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 262852.0,
      "end_time": 265176.0,
      "text": "go to school and give your students the best."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 265889.0,
      "end_time": 267564.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re a public-sector official,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 267588.0,
      "end_time": 271120.0,
      "text": "release the funds meant for that school or public health-care center"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 271144.0,
      "end_time": 274203.0,
      "text": "instead of stealing it for your personal purposes."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 275629.0,
      "end_time": 280402.0,
      "text": "By claiming that we have no power over our past, present and future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 280426.0,
      "end_time": 283895.0,
      "text": "we give too much authority to the wicked"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 283919.0,
      "end_time": 287568.0,
      "text": "who steal funds and beg God for forgiveness."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 289376.0,
      "end_time": 291441.0,
      "text": "Now for those of you who are not religious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 291465.0,
      "end_time": 293674.0,
      "text": "you also have to change your mindsets about us."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 294449.0,
      "end_time": 297106.0,
      "text": "There are many of us who are hardworking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 297130.0,
      "end_time": 299670.0,
      "text": "ethical and intellectual."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 299694.0,
      "end_time": 300945.0,
      "text": "It might surprise you."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 300969.0,
      "end_time": 303179.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 303203.0,
      "end_time": 304681.0,
      "text": "Now the second step"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 304706.0,
      "end_time": 308223.0,
      "text": "is that we have to utilize our resources and assets"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 308247.0,
      "end_time": 309397.0,
      "text": "for social impact."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 310520.0,
      "end_time": 311336.0,
      "text": "In England,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 311360.0,
      "end_time": 317267.0,
      "text": "1,900 churches have been shut down since 1969,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 317291.0,
      "end_time": 319918.0,
      "text": "due to shrinking congregations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 319942.0,
      "end_time": 322188.0,
      "text": "while in Africa, every single day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 322212.0,
      "end_time": 323890.0,
      "text": "a church or mosque is being built."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 324728.0,
      "end_time": 327808.0,
      "text": "In some communities, you might not find a public health center,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 327832.0,
      "end_time": 330257.0,
      "text": "a post office or even a school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 330281.0,
      "end_time": 331972.0,
      "text": "but you&#39;ll find a church or mosque."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 332842.0,
      "end_time": 336635.0,
      "text": "Some of these churches and mosques are world-class,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 336659.0,
      "end_time": 338645.0,
      "text": "with excellent audio-visual systems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 338669.0,
      "end_time": 340498.0,
      "text": "wonderful meeting spaces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 340523.0,
      "end_time": 343797.0,
      "text": "and they organize events that rival international concerts."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 344935.0,
      "end_time": 348853.0,
      "text": "The sad reality is that many of them are empty during the week."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 349939.0,
      "end_time": 351938.0,
      "text": "I live in the Lekki area of Lagos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 353264.0,
      "end_time": 356541.0,
      "text": "and in my community, there are at least 50 really nice churches,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 357708.0,
      "end_time": 360246.0,
      "text": "but there&#39;s no adult literacy center,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 360270.0,
      "end_time": 362159.0,
      "text": "no homeless shelter"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 362183.0,
      "end_time": 364854.0,
      "text": "and very few public schools and hospitals."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 365601.0,
      "end_time": 370139.0,
      "text": "Many of these spaces could be utilized for social change."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 371258.0,
      "end_time": 376210.0,
      "text": "Imagine if every single church in Lekki opened its doors"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 376235.0,
      "end_time": 377989.0,
      "text": "to the homeless at night,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 378130.0,
      "end_time": 382503.0,
      "text": "gave them a sleeping bag, a warm meal and a voucher in the morning"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 382528.0,
      "end_time": 384368.0,
      "text": "to learn a vocational course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 384392.0,
      "end_time": 387456.0,
      "text": "offered by the unemployed youth who attend that church."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 387480.0,
      "end_time": 390448.0,
      "text": "That would demonstrate what we preach"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 390472.0,
      "end_time": 393806.0,
      "text": "and what we speak about as people of faith,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 393831.0,
      "end_time": 397300.0,
      "text": "and what led me to Christianity in the first place."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 398675.0,
      "end_time": 404314.0,
      "text": "Similarly, we have to utilize our resources for social change."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 405506.0,
      "end_time": 409277.0,
      "text": "The 2016 \"why give\" survey conducted in Kenya"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 409301.0,
      "end_time": 415440.0,
      "text": "reveals that close to 60 percent of adults give to faith-based organizations --"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 415680.0,
      "end_time": 417532.0,
      "text": "even more than they give their extended families."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 418165.0,
      "end_time": 419614.0,
      "text": "This is not unique to Kenya."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 420681.0,
      "end_time": 422482.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s quite prevalent across Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 423395.0,
      "end_time": 427222.0,
      "text": "Many of our faith-based organizations have tremendous amounts of wealth"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 427246.0,
      "end_time": 429962.0,
      "text": "that can be utilized for social change."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 430990.0,
      "end_time": 434350.0,
      "text": "We have to check the sources of uses of these funds"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 434590.0,
      "end_time": 437943.0,
      "text": "and curb the excesses by our faith-based organizations."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 438607.0,
      "end_time": 442415.0,
      "text": "Now, this will require courage on the part of members,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 442439.0,
      "end_time": 446894.0,
      "text": "who will have to put their imams and priests on straight salaries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 446918.0,
      "end_time": 450376.0,
      "text": "require audited financial statements that will be published"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 451583.0,
      "end_time": 455452.0,
      "text": "and even reject contributions from unethical sources."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 456893.0,
      "end_time": 458420.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 458669.0,
      "end_time": 462660.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re already seeing positive examples in South Africa and Kenya,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 462900.0,
      "end_time": 463241.0,
      "text": "and the organizations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 463265.0,
      "end_time": 467510.0,
      "text": "such as the Africa Council for Accreditation and Accountability"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 467750.0,
      "end_time": 469337.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s checking faith-based organizations"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 469361.0,
      "end_time": 473241.0,
      "text": "and ensuring that they comply with biblical standards of stewardship."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 474824.0,
      "end_time": 476570.0,
      "text": "Now, the third step"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 476594.0,
      "end_time": 479284.0,
      "text": "is that we have to partner with all stakeholders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 479309.0,
      "end_time": 483127.0,
      "text": "and this is especially relevant for the non-religious in the audience."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 484240.0,
      "end_time": 488738.0,
      "text": "Recognizing the power and potential of faith-based organizations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 489752.0,
      "end_time": 492847.0,
      "text": "leveraging their assets, their scale,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 492871.0,
      "end_time": 495940.0,
      "text": "the public trust and credibility they have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 495119.0,
      "end_time": 496454.0,
      "text": "their lower operating costs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 496478.0,
      "end_time": 497964.0,
      "text": "their access to the grassroots"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 497988.0,
      "end_time": 499276.0,
      "text": "and their presence abroad."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 499802.0,
      "end_time": 501737.0,
      "text": "Politicians recognize this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 501761.0,
      "end_time": 506550.0,
      "text": "and campaign seasons are always filled with stops and picture opportunities"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 506790.0,
      "end_time": 507605.0,
      "text": "with leading faith leaders."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 508214.0,
      "end_time": 509675.0,
      "text": "Sadly, once elected,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 509699.0,
      "end_time": 513187.0,
      "text": "many of these faith-based organizations are ignored."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 513211.0,
      "end_time": 515616.0,
      "text": "And in fact, a World Bank survey revealed"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 515640.0,
      "end_time": 521409.0,
      "text": "that 30 to 70 percent of assets owned by medical organizations in Africa"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 521433.0,
      "end_time": 524380.0,
      "text": "are actually owned by faith-based organizations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 524620.0,
      "end_time": 528182.0,
      "text": "but that there&#39;s very little collaboration between the faith community"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 528206.0,
      "end_time": 530700.0,
      "text": "and public health-care systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 530835.0,
      "end_time": 533879.0,
      "text": "One positive example is from Ghana,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 533903.0,
      "end_time": 538352.0,
      "text": "where the Ghana Catholic Health Service partnered with a range of stakeholders"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 538376.0,
      "end_time": 544259.0,
      "text": "and was able to realize a 31 percent reduction in mortality."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 545470.0,
      "end_time": 548653.0,
      "text": "I believe there&#39;s so much potential that can be realized"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 548677.0,
      "end_time": 551605.0,
      "text": "when we walk across the divide of faith"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 551629.0,
      "end_time": 554436.0,
      "text": "and, hand in hand, try to solve many of our problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 555471.0,
      "end_time": 558744.0,
      "text": "Similarly, faith-based organizations can support the transfer"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 558768.0,
      "end_time": 560432.0,
      "text": "of critical skills and knowledge."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 560922.0,
      "end_time": 564175.0,
      "text": "Many of you in the NGO community or in the private sectors"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 564199.0,
      "end_time": 568872.0,
      "text": "realize how difficult it is to even attract 150 to 200 people"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 568897.0,
      "end_time": 570630.0,
      "text": "to your conferences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 570870.0,
      "end_time": 571978.0,
      "text": "sometimes even offering stipends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 572200.0,
      "end_time": 574103.0,
      "text": "reimbursements of transportation costs."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 574128.0,
      "end_time": 578613.0,
      "text": "Meanwhile, faith-based organizations draw thousands and millions"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 578637.0,
      "end_time": 580468.0,
      "text": "every Sunday or Friday ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 582770.0,
      "end_time": 585125.0,
      "text": "with the promise of a good sermon."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 586534.0,
      "end_time": 590367.0,
      "text": "The truth is we cannot address issues around family planning"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 590392.0,
      "end_time": 592680.0,
      "text": "without faith-based organizations in Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 593775.0,
      "end_time": 596435.0,
      "text": "Issues such as democratic rights and voter registration,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 596459.0,
      "end_time": 598959.0,
      "text": "ensuring that every member of a congregation"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 598983.0,
      "end_time": 600832.0,
      "text": "has a voter registration card,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 600856.0,
      "end_time": 603161.0,
      "text": "understands their democratic rights"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 603185.0,
      "end_time": 605179.0,
      "text": "and can exercise that."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 606291.0,
      "end_time": 609220.0,
      "text": "I really think it&#39;s critical that we consider partnering"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 609244.0,
      "end_time": 612155.0,
      "text": "with faith-based organizations to deliver social impact."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 613390.0,
      "end_time": 616891.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s also important to note that African faith-based organizations"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 616916.0,
      "end_time": 618699.0,
      "text": "have a strong presence globally."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 619324.0,
      "end_time": 623444.0,
      "text": "There are over 2,000 African nuns and priests in leadership positions"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 623468.0,
      "end_time": 624875.0,
      "text": "in Europe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 624899.0,
      "end_time": 628439.0,
      "text": "with more influence than some of our diplomatic envoys,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 628463.0,
      "end_time": 630733.0,
      "text": "operating at a fraction of the cost."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 630757.0,
      "end_time": 634250.0,
      "text": "They can serve as influencers and supporters."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 634274.0,
      "end_time": 637543.0,
      "text": "Similarly, some African churches have a presence"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 637567.0,
      "end_time": 639890.0,
      "text": "in countries across the globe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 639113.0,
      "end_time": 643566.0,
      "text": "and the Redeemed Christian Church of God has a presence in 196 countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 643590.0,
      "end_time": 646691.0,
      "text": "serving as a bridge to the diaspora and providing support."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 647461.0,
      "end_time": 651717.0,
      "text": "If our public-sector organizations could partner with these institutions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 651741.0,
      "end_time": 655487.0,
      "text": "we could unlock the potential of our diaspora populations."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 656986.0,
      "end_time": 660472.0,
      "text": "I know some of you are still struggling with this topic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 660496.0,
      "end_time": 662774.0,
      "text": "but I challenge you to think about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 662798.0,
      "end_time": 664996.0,
      "text": "A wise man once said, \"Faith is a risk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 666990.0,
      "end_time": 669191.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s a risk that I cannot afford not to take.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 669999.0,
      "end_time": 674375.0,
      "text": "I would suggest that partnerships with faith-based organizations are a risk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 674399.0,
      "end_time": 678984.0,
      "text": "but one that all stakeholders that are committed to social impact in Africa"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 679800.0,
      "end_time": 680683.0,
      "text": "cannot afford not to take."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 681942.0,
      "end_time": 685940.0,
      "text": "I often reflect on my conversation with that young boy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 685118.0,
      "end_time": 688348.0,
      "text": "and I believe I should have ended it a little differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 688372.0,
      "end_time": 691983.0,
      "text": "First, I should have commended him for asking tough questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 692537.0,
      "end_time": 695960.0,
      "text": "Africa needs more young people who challenge the status quo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 695984.0,
      "end_time": 697645.0,
      "text": "even in the faith communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 698698.0,
      "end_time": 701607.0,
      "text": "Secondly, I should have given him a little more hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 702830.0,
      "end_time": 703707.0,
      "text": "Not hope in the afterlife,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 703731.0,
      "end_time": 706795.0,
      "text": "but hope in Africa today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 706819.0,
      "end_time": 708800.0,
      "text": "because the faithful are powerful."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 709636.0,
      "end_time": 712978.0,
      "text": "Not just because of their beliefs but because of their assets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 713200.0,
      "end_time": 716803.0,
      "text": "their resources, their army of volunteers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 716827.0,
      "end_time": 721700.0,
      "text": "and because working together, across the divide,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 721940.0,
      "end_time": 726142.0,
      "text": "we can live as positive examples for what our children --"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 726166.0,
      "end_time": 727732.0,
      "text": "my children, your children --"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 727756.0,
      "end_time": 729448.0,
      "text": "deserve to see."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 729472.0,
      "end_time": 733640.0,
      "text": "An Africa that demonstrates that God loves Africans"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 733890.0,
      "end_time": 736602.0,
      "text": "and that we are just as capable as any other world region"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 736626.0,
      "end_time": 738216.0,
      "text": "in solving our problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 738240.0,
      "end_time": 739390.0,
      "text": "in peace ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 740314.0,
      "end_time": 741726.0,
      "text": "and love."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 743361.0,
      "end_time": 746170.0,
      "text": "I love this quote that says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 746194.0,
      "end_time": 751498.0,
      "text": "\"Hope is the ability to hear the melody of the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 752855.0,
      "end_time": 755879.0,
      "text": "Faith is the willingness and the courage"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 755903.0,
      "end_time": 757331.0,
      "text": "to dance to it today.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 758889.0,
      "end_time": 762985.0,
      "text": "I hope that we, as people of faith,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 763900.0,
      "end_time": 766715.0,
      "text": "can truly live up to the promise of social impact"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 766739.0,
      "end_time": 770298.0,
      "text": "that we have been called to do as change agents in society."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 771232.0,
      "end_time": 773326.0,
      "text": "And I believe that working with you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 773350.0,
      "end_time": 774601.0,
      "text": "all stakeholders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 774625.0,
      "end_time": 777677.0,
      "text": "we can truly solve Africa&#39;s most pressing challenges."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 778483.0,
      "end_time": 779689.0,
      "text": "I have that hope ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 780986.0,
      "end_time": 782931.0,
      "text": "and I have the faith,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 782955.0,
      "end_time": 784601.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;ve started to dance."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 784625.0,
      "end_time": 785866.0,
      "text": "Won&#39;t you join me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 785890.0,
      "end_time": 787400.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 787650.0,
      "end_time": 791230.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}